                  <span xml:lang="en" target="#URFA-539_a9" xml:id="a20">He said, “I see you have prescribed an anthelmintic pill for me. My hand is broken, why did you prescribe an anthelmintic?”(The doctor) replied, “How did you break your hand?”</span>
               </spanGrp>
